2006-08-22  Takuro Ashie <ashie@homa.ne.jp>

	* po/ChangeLog: Added to pass make dist.
	* test/Makefile.am: Add .tomoe-config.xml.
	* src/tomoe_window.c: Add #warning FIXME! to remain to fix the
	procedure of loading config files later.
	Recommended procedure is:
	  1. load a debug config.xml (if a debug environment variable is set).
	  2. load ~/.tomoe/config.xml.
	  3. load /etc/tomoe/config.xml.
	(Younger number has higher priority.)

